tic notions he holds on attainment, vehicle, and even gender.\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":1323,\"end\":1395}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"882d9131-8f6a-4d51-9898-52f7d0dba530\",\"sort\":198,\"type\":\"introduction\",\"label\":\"i.6\",\"alignments\":{}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":957,\"uuid\":\"882d9131-8f6a-4d51-9898-52f7d0dba530\"},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"The seventh chapter opens with \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":31}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Vimalakīrti\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":31,\"end\":42},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"b9ca12fb-e3be-4924-ad28-b09e52530acb\",\"uuid\":\"bf6be743-7b2a-4db2-b815-2e8f5ddfe7ef\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" answering \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":42,\"end\":53}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Mañjuśrī\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":53,\"end\":61},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"10b56931-f8ef-48df-9532-76c888687d0f\",\"uuid\":\"a58bec90-758f-472d-a5c2-342407a1323f\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"’s leading questions to explain that whatever ways a \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":61,\"end\":114}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"bodhisattva\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":114,\"end\":125},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c72eb4f3-700e-454d-996e-5ccdba29e6be\",\"uuid\":\"8cf0d2d3-0600-48b3-ad79-6773b4914ee8\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" might follow, including those conventionally considered the most negative and harmful, will cause him to attain the qualities of the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":125,\"end\":259}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"buddhas\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":259,\"end\":266},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9b76e3ce-41f6-4da3-89a2-722141c90c1e\",\"uuid\":\"e896134a-8bc0-44e6-b72a-003a62c1487e\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". This leads to a discussion on the \",\"a