ether in reverence. He taught them the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":308,\"end\":441}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Dharma\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":441,\"end\":447},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c08db6f5-393e-4ec4-bf72-4043e53b3129\",\"uuid\":\"93907f8a-dd91-4496-8a7e-26b706491f30\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", and they all attained the stage of irreversibility\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":447,\"end\":499},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"endNoteLink\",\"attrs\":{\"notes\":[{\"endNote\":\"8155277b-4152-462e-9a9e-fea03235db4c\",\"label\":\"73\",\"uuid\":\"15921a85-11a1-4476-a857-8f17d93fee42\",\"start\":499,\"end\":499,\"location\":\"end\",\"toh\":null}]}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" from unexcelled, perfect \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":499,\"end\":525}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"enlightenment\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":525,\"end\":538},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"62f923c5-8dfa-4620-8dec-7bb032231bf7\",\"uuid\":\"4eea95e0-e52b-4a79-aa36-e1ff7bc70293\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\". It occurred to me then, ‘The disciples, who do not know the thoughts or the inclinations of others, are not able to teach the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":538,\"end\":666}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Dharma\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":666,\"end\":672},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"c08db6f5-393e-4ec4-bf72-4043e53b3129\",\"uuid\":\"86384c4c-5527-4e39-9bbf-f655e97e503b\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" to anyone. Why? These disciples are not expert in discerning the superiority and inferiority of the spiritual faculties of living beings, and they are not always in a state of \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":672,\"end\":849}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"concentration\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":849,\"end\":862},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"7c9b18c2-de43-42af-9b86-2cadc11acbf8\",\"uuid\":\"1c9fd598-4324-4845-848e-d4352dc64dc1\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\" like the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":862,\"end\":872}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Tathāgata\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":872,\"end\":881},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"e708dad0-3dd7-49b0-8de3-b2e34b3f8d08\",\"uuid\":\"15c2614f-e277-4973-9825-633915566d04\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", the \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":881,\"end\":887}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"arhat\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":887,\"end\":892},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"8584345b-bf7d-481b-ac82-4146d2374b3c\",\"uuid\":\"b435a023-5836-4c40-9bfc-51a82ee41239\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", the perfectly accomplished \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":892,\"end\":921}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Buddha\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":921,\"end\":927},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"9b76e3ce-41f6-4da3-89a2-722141c90c1e\",\"uuid\":\"4122768e-81a2-45df-9b12-8bedd044286e\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\".’ Therefore, \",\"attrs\":{\"start\":927,\"end\":941}},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\"Lord\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":941,\"end\":945},\"marks\":[{\"type\":\"glossaryInstance\",\"attrs\":{\"glossary\":\"41c623b8-3d94-4f8e-b2c5-1d7a5f5af6d3\",\"uuid\":\"51c519c1-168b-4e5c-ac69-9b113fdcc7ff\",\"toh\":null}}]},{\"type\":\"text\",\"text\":\", I am reluctant to go to that good man to inquire about his health.”\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":945,\"end\":1014}}]}]},{\"type\":\"passage\",\"attrs\":{\"uuid\":\"e24677c7-627b-46ce-bef0-4d826f3dd634\",\"sort\":2545,\"type\":\"translation\",\"label\":\"3.25\",\"alignments\":{\"toh176\":{\"folioUuid\":\"b407a734-73e9-497a-8433-c7740e6413e7\",\"toh\":\"toh176\",\"tibetan\":\"$27\",\"folioNumber\":188,\"volumeNumber\":60}}},\"content\":[{\"type\":\"paragraph\",\"attrs\":{\"start\":0,\"end\":127,\"uuid\":\"d2eb56f8-83d0-4871-af2f-936fcc0ccd01\",\"hasLeadingSpace\":true,\"leadingSpaceUuid\":\"e9d05d2c-721